name: BLOOM SUMMARY VOL.1
description:
this is a special edition of the first to ninth minting collection, collages merged into one for the tenth edition. The collage summary edition will be printed every 10th minting and multiples thereof. 

Here "BLOOM SUMMARY VOL.1"! Yeay!!

How this is special, because this collage is a sweet journey in the process, the story and the end result. 

All of these trips were precious to me, without exception.

Thank you all my friends and U on this journey. You guys are really sweet. Like candy that never runs out to eat. Soft and so magical!!

and 

The flower in your hand is still blooming and smiling, keep it up honey! 

Lav!!!
